f=Governance/DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md · s=Governance department makes business's rules real: **board** rules decisions brought gate (constitution, locked strategy, spend thresholds, risk), **precedent** makes rulings durable binding-by-default (record, retrieve, apply-or-distinguish, silent inconsistency), **sentinel** covers everything never asked review (output sweeps, gate-bypass audits, audit trails runs on). Board leader carries department identity (principled-gatekeeper). department's authority entirely derivative enforces documents operator wrote thresholds operator set; final calls always sit operator. · p=Solve three ways governance fails practice: rules enforced convenient (board's gate non-negotiable constitutional rulings cited everything), rulings don't bind future (precedent's distinguish-or-overrule discipline), gates measure what walks through them (sentinel's coverage guarantee). Works any scale small Canadian business sets $1K gate 3-article constitution; funded venture sets $50K stricter floors. skills, different config. · ws=`OPERATOR \· (writes the constitution & commitments; sets thresholds; makes final calls; \· holds the stop button; amends what board enforces) \· ↑ \· ┌──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────┐` · wt:(who consumes whom)=**precedent wraps board**: retrieval apply/distinguish run before board rules; consistency-check tests proposed ruling; capture records final one (including operator overrules). One shared decision log board-config's `decision_log_destination` single source truth; precedent sentinel point it, never fork it., **sentinel feeds board**: VIOLATION classifications BYPASS/PARTIAL findings escalate formal rulings (constitution-enforcement retroactive full gate). Sentinel detects; board rules; operator remediates., **sentinel's trails carry everyone**: audit-trail-design's practices (append-only, who/what/when/basis, integrity checks) govern precedent's log hygiene watchers' events., **Cross-department**: marcus improves proposals before submission (decision-critic) owns strategy process sets locked commitments (with operator); board enforces, never amends. Vista's flagged roadmap decisions echo's commitments enter gate like any decision they qualify. Bypass-pattern process fixes route configured process owner future Ops agent; operator until then). · wi=**Documents first.** Nothing department works until operator writes constitution (template: board/custom/constitution-enforcement/assets/) locked commitments (template: board/custom/strategic-veto/assets/) fills board-config's thresholds. Unfilled skill stops-and-asks degrades loudly; nothing ever defaulted inferred. **A decision arrives gate.** Precedent surfaces top-3 prior rulings (apply/distinguish made explicit). Board runs sequence constitution veto fiduciary (if spend) pre-mortem (major/untested) risk matrix early exits: VIOLATION VETO end review immediately, stated path (change decision; amend operator/marcus; re-scope). **Before finalizing**, consistency-check tests proposed ruling against precedent: conflicts distinguished (material difference named) overruled (justified, cross-marked, operator-flagged). Never silent. **Every ruling captured** precedent's schema rationale mandatory, tags grown invented, operator overrules recorded instructive entries. Append-only, corrections reference. **Continuously (per configured cadences)**, sentinel sweeps outputs (warn near-boundary; freeze-recommend escalate violations immediately, never batched) scans executed actions bypasses (retroactive review root cause: criteria gap friction workaround different fixes; patterns process-fix proposals). Coverage stated report; unsampled never clear. **Patterns upward cadence**: repeated overrules one article (amendment pressure), operator-vs-board splits, drift curves, repeat bypass routes surfaced operator marcus's strategy reviews. Governance surfaces; strategy decides. **Rule 0.6 standing flag.** three logical/ folders placeholders (board: decision analysis governance standards; precedent: legal reasoning/precedent doctrine CBR; sentinel: audit sampling statistical process control last shares ground vista's statistics domain, coordinate source choice). Until filled: P×I rubric, retrieval similarity judgment, coverage claims honest-but-informal output says so. tested scripts (fiduciary_check, risk_matrix) computed framework-level. · ds=\| Agent \| Skills \| Identity \| Operational \| Logical \| agent.md \| · ds=\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · ds=\| board \| 5/5 (2 scripts tested, 2 templates) \| principled-gatekeeper-charlie-munger (leader) \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| current \| · ds=\| precedent \| 3/3 (case-law-method converted marketplace→custom, flagged) \| intentionally empty \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| current \| · ds=\| sentinel \| 3/3 (1 verbatim marketplace) \| intentionally empty \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| current \| · ds=Department complete 2026-07-07. Pending, named: operator's constitution locked commitments config fill-ins (the department structurally done dormant until exist); three logical source books; sweep automation (future 5.2 proposal); shared OS-level skill layer.